title: Tin Tin Vegetarian Food - 1st Avenue Mall
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Chinese, International, Western, Take-out
description: Vegetarian vendor in food court called Magic Kitchen. Menu includes soups, rice dishes, noodles and veggie versions of continental dishes including veggie fish and chips. Seating is shared with other vendors. Another branch is in Gurney Plaza.
